{
  "stem": "13382.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- at that time, I was about 17 years old-- or 16 or 17.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was very anxious to do something, to help something.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I went with father.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I went on my own.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And at one time, there was-- I was with father.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was some sort of a chemical factory.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They were producing a substitute soap, because everything is scarce.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You know, at that time, you couldn't get any-- and some cheap cosmetics.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So I just you know, went into it, I said, listen.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I would like to sell your products.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he gave me a sample of products.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took it back to Fil'akovo.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was a huge sort of a department store type of thing who were serving the-- the laborers from the-- it actually, it belonged to the-- to the factory.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I get a huge orders.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I was earning money on it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said that's-- that's a very good idea.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But so when they got the goods, there was some substitute soap.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And there was nothing but water in something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So they put-- put on the shelves to dry out.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then they ended up nothing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- [LAUGHS] --I mean, obviously it was a sort of a fraud or some sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I stopped doing them at all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And one thing got clear to us-- all of us-- that with doing nothing in Fil'akovo where we are, and being sort of exposed to people-- they knew exactly that we are Jewish, and so we had to-- the best thing if we move to Budapest.",
      "word_count": 46
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Because we had much more-- much more prospect of-- of-- of doing something, or making some money, or-- or-- or being out of the focus of-- of other people.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
